Download Podman CLI
https://podman.io


Initialize podman via the commnand below and follow the instructions after initialization.
After installing, the below command will create and start your first Podman machine.

podman machine init


After starting your first Podman machine via "podman machine start," following the commands below to clone the MalDoc repo:


1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/JemHadar/MalDocAnalysisContainer.git
cd MalDocAnalysisContainer

This directory includes the Dockerfile and related build context.


Add the executable flag to the shell script; execute it and pass the file to be analyzed as an argument

./podman_mal_doc.sh maldoc